  "contentHtml": "\n    \n    \n        \n                <ul>\n                    \n                     <li><a href=\"/news/hospitals\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hospitals</a></li>                     <li>1 min read</li>                 </ul>\n                            \n        \n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Online Bureau\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                    <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On Mar 13, 2026 at 12:21 PM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>Hyderabad: <a href=\"/tag/medicover+hospitals\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Medicover Hospitals</a> has inaugurated a 550-bed multi-specialty hospital in the Financial District of Hyderabad, marking the group’s <a href=\"/tag/25th+hospital+in+india\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">25th hospital in India</a> and expanding its presence in one of the country’s fastest-growing healthcare markets.The newly launched facility, offers comprehensive healthcare services across multiple specialties and is equipped with advanced diagnostic and treatment technologies.<!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->A key highlight of the hospital is the introduction of rapid <a href=\"/tag/cardiac+scanning+technology\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">cardiac scanning technology</a> capable of completing heart scans in about five seconds, being introduced for the first time in the Telangana and Andhra Pradesh. The hospital is also equipped with 640-slice CT scan technology, enabling faster and more precise diagnosis.\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        Inaugurating the hospital Anumula Revanth Reddy, Chief Minister of Telangana said, \"Hyderabad continues to strengthen its position as a major healthcare hub and that the addition of advanced medical infrastructure will improve healthcare access for people across the state.\"                    \n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Online Bureau</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Mar 13, 2026 at 12:21 PM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Mar 13, 2026 at 12:21 PM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">1 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n        